    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    ArrayList<D>
    Dynamic Array implementation of the List data structure
    ArrayQueue<D>
    Dynamic Circular Array implementation of the Queue data structure
    ArrayStack<D>
    Dynamic Array implementation of the Stack data structure
    AVLDictionary<K,D>
    Implementation of the Dictionary data structure with underlying AVL Tree representation.
    AVLTree<K,D>
    AVL Tree implementation
    BinarySearchTree<K,D>
    Binary Search Tree implementation
    BinaryTree<K,D>
    This abstract class provides a skeletal implementation of the BinaryTree data structure in which only the BTNode.class class and the traversal methods are implemented
    DHeap<K,D>
    Implementation using d-heap of a generic Priority Queue data structure composed of nodes of type DHeapNode containing pairs of data objects associated with a key
    DHeapNode<K,D>
    Implementation of the node of a d-heap implementation of a generic Priority Queue data structure containing pairs of data objects associated with a key
    Dictionary<K,D>
    Interface for a Dictionary data structure that maps keys to data values.
    DoubleEndedList<D>
    Double-ended Linked List implementation of the List, Stack and Queue data structures
    Edge<D>
    Interface for the edge of a generic Graph data structure with vertexes containing data objects
    EdgeAL<D>
    Implementation of the edges of a generic Graph data structure composed of vertexes of type VertexAL containing data objects and implemented using Adjacent Lists.
    Graph<D>
    Interface for a generic Graph data structure composed of vertexes of type Vertex containing data objects and edges of type Edge
    GraphAL<D>
    Implementation using Adjacent Lists of a generic Graph data structure composed of vertexes of type VertexAL containing data objects and edges of type EdgeAL
    HashTable<K,D>
    Implementation of the Dictionary data structure using an underlying Hash Table, where collisions are handled using chaining (via a Singly Linked List).
    List<D>
    Interface for a generic List data structure
    PriorityQueue<K,D>
    Interface for a generic Priority Queue data structure composed of nodes of type PriorityQueueNode containing pairs of data objects associated with a key
    PriorityQueueNode<K,D>
    Interface for the node of a generic Priority Queue data structure containing pairs of data objects associated with a key
    Queue<D>
    Interface for a generic Queue data structure
    QuickFind<D>
    Implementation of a generic Union Find data structure composed of nodes of type QuickFindNode containing data objects, based on Quick Find.
    QuickFindNode<D>
    Implementation of the node of a generic Union Find data structure containing data objects based on the Quick Find implementation.
    QuickFindSize<D>
    Implementation of a generic Union Find data structure composed of nodes of type QuickFindSizeNode containing data objects, based on Quick Find with heuristic on the size: the implementation of union checks what is the shortest list to concatenate and updates the pointers to the root only for its elements.
    QuickFindSizeNode<D>
    Implementation of the node of a generic Union Find data structure containing data objects based on the Quick Find implementation with heuristic on the size.
    QuickUnion<D>
    Implementation of a generic Union Find data structure composed of nodes of type QuickUnionNode containing data objects, based on Quick Union.
    QuickUnionNode<D>
    Implementation of the node of a generic Union Find data structure containing data objects based on the Quick Union implementation.
    QuickUnionRank<D>
    Implementation of a generic Union Find data structure composed of nodes of type QuickUnionRankNode containing data objects, based on Quick Union with heuristic on the rank: the implementation of union avoids to improve the rank when it is possible.
    QuickUnionRankNode<D>
    Implementation of the node of a generic Union Find data structure containing data objects based on the Quick Union implementation with heuristic on the rank.
    Sorting
    This class contains various sorting algorithms
    Stack<D>
    Interface for a generic Stack data structure
    Tree<K,D>
    Interface for a generic Tree data structure
    UnionFind<D>
    Interface for a generic Union Find data structure composed of nodes of type UnionFindNode containing data objects
    UnionFindNode<D>
    Interface for the node of a generic Union Find data structure containing data objects
    Vertex<D>
    Interface for the vertex of a generic Graph data structure containing data objects
    VertexAL<D>
    Implementation of the vertexes containing data objects of a generic Graph data structure composed of edges of type EdgeAL and implemented using Adjacent Lists.
